{"title":"冬天的犁铧（外一首）","authors":["李华"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的犁铧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见冬天的犁铧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是杨柳依依"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵朵野花开败了寒冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见那些扶犁的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下淌着春水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双眼睛里常有燕子飞过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双大手摊开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一块滚烫的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的犁铧从墙上走下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步比节气更快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见一浪高过一浪的泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把热气腾腾的乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进了我的诗里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块块锈迹隐去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天在镰刀上亮了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮了的还有农人不眠的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光下的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟透的日子愈加饱满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞激动的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南风吹拂面对翻滚的庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们收获着黄金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边的圆月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正从我们的腰身上走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处灯火的村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在镰刀下起伏"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}